<ul>
	<li>
		Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Computer Science or related field.</li>
	<li>
		5 or more years of experience leading architecture of enterprise-class Java platforms and construction initiatives</li>
	<li>
		Experience with data processing, analytics &amp; segmentation systems</li>
	<li>
		Fluent in the object-oriented development and applicable Java technologies</li>
	<li>
		Fluent in JBoss application server configuration, deployment, management and environment design</li>
	<li>
		Experience in architecting RESTful API services</li>
	<li>
		Familiar with NoSQL databases, Mongo a huge plus</li>
	<li>
